ingredients.ingredient: 1 (8 ounce) package phyllo dough, thawed if frozen
½ (13 ounce) jar chocolate-hazelnut spread (such as Nutella®)

cookingTips: Keep phyllo dough covered with damp towel while working to prevent drying
Brush each sheet lightly with butter to avoid excessive oiliness
Roll tightly and seal ends with dab of butter to prevent unraveling during baking
enrichment.coachingPrompt: Teach the user proper phyllo handling techniques to create crispy, golden cigars with melty chocolate hazelnut centers.
